results.description:
Live Well Laugh Often Love Much/Stacked Blocks/Accent Piece/Wooden Block Set/Sign Blocks/Shelf Sitter
DETAILS

Item Pictured:
This is a set of three solid wood blocks featuring a primitive country saying. The blocks are stained and then painted in barn red on the fronts and distressed by hand for a rustic primitive look. The saying is painted in white as shown. Painting is done by hand without the use of stencils, etc. The set is then finished with a clear finish spray. The overall measurement of the set is approximately 4 1/2” tall by 8" wide. The sizes of the individual blocks are 1½” tall x 4” long, 1½” tall by 6” long, and 1½” tall x 8” long. Each block is 1½” thick. The blocks are glued and nailed together to form a single set. 

The lettering is painted completely by hand. No stencils are ever used, nor do we use any vinyl with our products. These blocks are made to order so the ones you receive may vary slightly from the picture but will be almost identical. 

It is not uncommon for the natural character of the wood to be seen on these blocks. Examples of this are knots and wood grain. We make no attempt to cover any knots or imperfections. 

Turnaround time: 
Your blocks will be made once ordered. All sets CAN take up to 1 week; however, we typically process orders within 1-3 days plus the shipping time. For rush orders, please contact us directly.

Shipping:
All orders are shipped via UPS or USPS. Please remember to take into consideration shipping transit time when ordering. All orders ship from Georgia. We work extremely hard to get orders shipped as quickly as possible. Please expect a week from the time you place the order for your order to ship. If you need your order sooner, please contact us and we will work extremely hard to meet your deadline. Please double check your shipping address when ordering. We cannot be responsible for items shipped to addresses provided incorrectly.
